01:50:35.570 --> 01:50:39.280
the takeaway is that getting
sufficient levels of EPA

01:50:39.280 --> 01:50:42.810
and particularly there's 300
milligram threshold of DHA,

01:50:42.810 --> 01:50:46.760
plus, if you are interested
in it and it's right for you,

01:50:46.760 --> 01:50:48.970
200 milligrams of phosphatidylserine

01:50:48.970 --> 01:50:50.440
can be an important augment

01:50:50.440 --> 01:50:53.510
for improving the symptoms of ADHD.

01:50:53.510 --> 01:50:55.400
You'll also find literature out there

01:50:55.400 --> 01:50:59.290
