01:52:44.940 --> 01:52:45.880
Regardless of price

01:52:45.880 --> 01:52:48.635
people are taking
Modafinil and armodafinil.

01:52:48.635 --> 01:52:52.550
Want to emphasize that
unlike Ritalin and Adderall,

01:52:52.550 --> 01:52:56.330
Modafinil and armodafinil
are weak dopamine

01:52:56.330 --> 01:52:57.780
re-uptake inhibitors,

01:52:57.780 --> 01:53:00.150
and that's how they lead
to increases in dopamine.

01:53:00.150 --> 01:53:02.610
So, whereas Ritalin and
Adderall, amphetamine,

01:53:02.610 --> 01:53:05.340
and cocaine lead to big
increases in dopamine

01:53:05.340 --> 01:53:07.910
also through re-uptake
mechanisms and so forth

01:53:07.910 --> 01:53:12.830
Modafinil is a weaker
dopamine re-uptake stimulator

01:53:12.830 --> 01:53:15.150
and so what that means is that it leaves

01:53:15.150 --> 01:53:17.750
more dopamine around to
be active at the synopsis,

01:53:17.750 --> 01:53:19.910
the gaps between neurons,

01:53:19.910 --> 01:53:22.090
however, it also activates other systems.

01:53:22.090 --> 01:53:24.280
It acts on the orexin system,

01:53:24.280 --> 01:53:26.430
which is actually a peptide
that we talked about

01:53:26.430 --> 01:53:28.450
in the episode on hunger,

01:53:28.450 --> 01:53:31.130
because it regulates hunger and appetite,

01:53:31.130 --> 01:53:34.340
and it regulates sleepiness
and feelings of sleepiness.

01:53:34.340 --> 01:53:36.140
In fact, the, excuse me, orexin

01:53:36.140 --> 01:53:37.740
also called hypocretin system,

01:53:37.740 --> 01:53:39.360
the orexin hypocretin system

01:53:39.360 --> 01:53:42.060
is what's disrupted in narcolepsy.

01:53:42.060 --> 01:53:44.430
That was the important
discovery of my colleagues,

01:53:44.430 --> 01:53:46.630
Emmanuel Mignot and Seiji Nishino

01:53:46.630 --> 01:53:48.370
at Stanford some years ago,

01:53:48.370 --> 01:53:50.990
they identified the
biological basis of narcolepsy

01:53:50.990 --> 01:53:54.840
and it's a disruption in the
so orexin hypocretin system

01:53:54.840 --> 01:53:56.350
and Modafinil is one of the

01:53:56.350 --> 01:53:58.140
primary treatments for narcolepsy.

01:53:58.140 --> 01:54:01.640
It also has these other
effects on the dopamine system

01:54:01.640 --> 01:54:03.930
and on the norepinephrine system,

01:54:03.930 --> 01:54:08.500
even though it doesn't lead
to quite as intense levels

01:54:08.500 --> 01:54:11.380
of dopamine and arousal and focus,

01:54:11.380 --> 01:54:14.027
it does have the property of
raising levels of attention

01:54:14.027 --> 01:54:16.190
and focus, and that's
why people are using it.

01:54:16.190 --> 01:54:19.697
So it's a somewhat
milder form of Adderall.

01:54:19.697 --> 01:54:22.796
Armodafinil for some people
works as well as Modafinil

01:54:22.796 --> 01:54:23.880
and as I mentioned before,

01:54:23.880 --> 01:54:26.260
it's much lower cost for
